#: ../../SO3.md:510
msgid ""
"Where there is a positive correlation/relationship between vulnerability and"
" the factor[^3] (i.e., if the factor value increases, vulnerability also "
"increases), the data should be normalized using the equation below:"
msgstr ""
"وحيثما كان هناك ارتباط/علاقة إيجابية بين قابلية التأثير والعامل[^ 3] (أي أنه"
